          <p>2011</p>

          <strong>BS in Radio Technical Services in Radio Technical Services</strong>
          <br>
          Yekaterinburg Engineering Technical School - Yekaterinburg, RU <br>
          2001
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
